---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-[#151515]/5 bg-[#FAFAF7] px-6 py-20 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <span class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#151515] uppercase">
          Bellezza<span class="text-[#B88746]">.</span>
        </span>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#151515]/60">
          Redefinindo o conceito de beleza e autocuidado em um ambiente de absoluto luxo e tranquilidade.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#B88746]">Serviços</h4>
        <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-sm text-[#151515]/70">
          <li>Cabelo & Coloração</li>
          <li>Estética Facial</li>
          <li>Manicure & Pedicure</li>
          <li>Massagem Terapêutica</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#B88746]">Localização</h4>
        <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-sm text-[#151515]/70">
          <li>Rua Oscar Freire, 1400</li>
          <li>Jardins, São Paulo - SP</li>
          <li>(11) 98888-8888</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#B88746]">Horários</h4>
        <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-sm text-[#151515]/70">
          <li>Ter - Sáb: 09h às 19h</li>
          <li>Dom - Seg: Fechado</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 border-t border-[#151515]/5 pt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-6 sm:flex-row">
      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[#151515]/40">
        © {currentYear} Bellezza Premium. Todos os direitos reservados.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <a href="#" class="text-[#151515]/40 hover:text-[#B88746] transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line></svg></a>
        <a href="#" class="text-[#151515]/40 hover:text-[#B88746] transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
